"TO ALL GUARD PERSONNEL:

This kitchen is NOT a self-service restaurant! If you are hungry, go to the mess room or kindly ask one of the servants to get something to eat for you. The kitchen is supposed to be clean and tidy all the time. The lord does not want people with muddy boots trampling around in here and touching everything with their dirty hands.

The next person I catch helping himself to a snack in here will feel my SKILLET on his HEAD!

The cook"